{"tid":531342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最強c朗佔全隊的7成射門","createTime":"2018-01-16T16:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T13:58:43.000Z","uid":68628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c0182cb9e6ed58a4f09e3374f648c8566a508858","tid":531342,"uid":68628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T16:48:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>過去十年最差的入球率</strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">◆轉貼請註明來自皇馬球迷俱樂部<a href=\"http://www.Rmfans.Com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.Rmfans.Com&d=Dxp51rT0QgXQJyfURqq9Q49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=25a39fd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.Rmfans.Com</a></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"http://bbs.rmfans.com/data/attachment/forum/201801/16/131736r76vpw7dw36p6f3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.rmfans.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201801%2F16%2F131736r76vpw7dw36p6f3w.jpg&h=be32eaef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在本賽季聯賽中皇馬已經創造了125次射門</span>，這是20支球隊中的第二多，施丹的球隊在本賽季聯賽中的入球率是過去10年來最差的。<br />\n<br />\n施丹抱怨皮球不進龍門，他拒絶因此批評他的球員。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬本賽季的問題不僅僅是無法轉化射門為入球，不過至少在場上這是一個嚴重的問題。卡斯米路也表示球隊在入球方面的運氣實在是很差，在一場比賽後他接受採訪時曾說：&ldquo;我們缺少的是入球，我們總是無法得分，一整年來這困擾著我們，很難解釋是什麼原因。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n皇馬在創造機會方面沒有問題，他們每場比賽平均完成了19次射門，場均射正6次，射正率39%；他們在聯賽的前19場比賽中攻入了32個入球，場均1.77球；但與上賽季的場均2.7球，或者與摩連奴時代2011-12賽季的場均3.1球相比就顯得有點不盡如人意。<br />\n<br />\n更衣室裡有一種觀點認為，頻繁的傷患影響了球員的入球，巴利和賓施馬在本賽季缺席了很大部分時間。<br />\n<br />\n上賽季的皇馬入球不斷，但本賽季則不是如此；在本賽季聯賽的下半場皇馬只取得了9個入球，在每場比賽的最後五分鐘0入球。<br />\n<br />\n假如球隊可以攻入更多入球，那麼他們就會更接近榜首，這是公平的。"},{"pid":"331a59f89aed741b11525f094106b539b1c9e1c1","tid":531342,"uid":24926,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"C朗入得太小"},{"pid":"10f8c950ecb8c275eee767cd1ffcb34b3bef2bad","tid":531342,"uid":85163,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c36210e4591ac6c73a39a258a9af1f951adb468","tid":531342,"uid":2290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"假如球隊可以攻入更多入球，那麼他們就會更接近榜首，這是公平的。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太廢話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdde97883a327f65bfa2dd9c455a1775880ac8f","tid":531342,"uid":129862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:34:24.000Z","msg":"除左賤迷 個個都知原因啦"},{"pid":"56209de4de598b9d47f158f6ce90d72ff6e9a37c","tid":531342,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T19:16:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾朗點解救唔到全家？"},{"pid":"5ebc643ff78ba4ee9826cf54f0cbee772bee2fb9","tid":531342,"uid":68628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T19:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你賓周馬</blockquote><br />\n最衰賓周馬成日敗家 搞到入唔到波 仆街黎"},{"pid":"5c2a11d949eae73df61ea5966625542512916634","tid":531342,"uid":135060,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T19:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/033814_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F033814_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=7044afc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52d2597c900c46df22298953d6d6c384ccf4f032","tid":531342,"uid":7199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>過去十年最差的入球率</strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">◆轉貼請註明來自皇馬球迷俱樂部<a href=\"http://www.Rmfans.Com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.Rmfans.Com&d=Dxp51rT0QgXQJyfURqq9Q49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=25a39fd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.Rmfans.Com</a></span></div